## Release Notes

- Add snyk security check to required checks for PRs. @iphydf (#25)
- Add CODEOWNERS and settings.yml files. @iphydf (#14)
- Migrate java dependencies to rules_jvm_external. @iphydf (#13)
- Add windows native dependency. @iphydf (#12)
- Add bazel rule for echobot test. @iphydf (#11)
- Format yaml files according to yamllint's requirements. @iphydf (#9)
- Enable .travis.yml check and use non-markdown license. @iphydf (#8)
- Add README.md; we now have a test that checks for it. @iphydf (#7)
- Add a bazel test that ensures all our projects are GPL-3.0. @iphydf (#6)
- Use "native" target for jvm-toxcore-c. @iphydf (#5)
- Relicense under GPLv3. @iphydf (#4)
- Avoid clashes with "build" directories on case-insensitive file systems. @iphydf (#3)
- Add bazel build script for echobot-jvm. @iphydf (#2)
- Add appveyor configuration for echobot-jvm. @iphydf (#1)
